  4005	# 44. Frontend Action Availability Contract
  4006	
  4007	Every detail endpoint should optionally return `available_actions`.
  4008	
  4009	Example:
  4010	
  4011	```json
  4012	{
  4013	  "available_actions": [
  4014	    {
  4015	      "action_code": "submit",
  4016	      "label": "Submit Application",
  4017	      "enabled": false,
